                        </ol>
                    </nav>
                    <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold text-white mb-4">Secure & Compliant</h1>
                    <p class="lead text-white-50 mb-4">Bank-level encryption, IOLTA compliant trust accounting, and secure client portal. Your data and your clients' data protected.</p>
